data.description: This 4 Bedroom with an office & 2 1/2 Bath Pool Home is looking for its new family!!  The home sits on a nice corner lot completely fenced in with white vinyl fencing with a side double gate for easy access with a nice size side yard to add in a play set, park an RV, boat or outdoor parties!! A beautiful family retreat offering privacy and space for everyone! This concrete block home features a screen enclosed heated pool and patio, new pool pump and filter 2022, vinyl and tile flooring through out, A/C 2020, New roof installed in 2019, new appliances refrigerator, stove, microwave, dishwasher in 2021 the kitchen has 2 pantries. Also to boot .... Hurricane Shutters for all windows come with this lovely home!! The primary suite is huge with his and her closets with bathtub and a separate walk in shower, not lacking any room here!! Nice size two car garage and in-home laundry and cabinets, plenty of work space.  Home is centrally located within minutes to the Intracoastal Waterway to launch your boat, fish or just enjoy the views of nature.  Minutes to I 95, to go most anywhere you want to travel to.  Minutes to the Atlantic Ocean, NSB, Schools, Library, Restaurants, Shopping, Hospitals and so much more!!  No damage or flooding at all from last years storms.  This is one home you want to see!!  All information is deemed corrected but not guaranteed. ;Water: City
